What you need to know:

This will be the second game for the Rising Stars since the competition kicked-off last weekend and will be played at Sheikh Amri Abeid stadium in Arusha from 1pmKenya beat Ethiopia 3-0 in their opening game on Monday after teenage sensation Benson Omala, striker Ronald Reagan and midfielder Enock Wanyama netted to send the team top of the groupEthiopia beat Sudan 3-2 in a thrilling match on Wednesday to keep Rising Stars on toes in this group which Sudan sits bottom without a point